From: Yunguo Wei <yunguo.wei@windriver.com>
Date: Fri, 9 Mar 2018 10:02:47 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] rtlwifi: enable the capacity of switching networking
 namespace

Signed-off-by: Yunguo Wei <yunguo.wei@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/realtek/rtlwifi/base.c | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/realtek/rtlwifi/base.c b/drivers/net/wireless/realtek/rtlwifi/base.c
index bdc3791..6ec35ba 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/realtek/rtlwifi/base.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/realtek/rtlwifi/base.c
@@ -416,6 +416,8 @@ static void _rtl_init_mac80211(struct ieee80211_hw *hw)
 
 	hw->wiphy->flags |= WIPHY_FLAG_HAS_REMAIN_ON_CHANNEL;
 
+	hw->wiphy->flags |= WIPHY_FLAG_NETNS_OK;
+
 	hw->wiphy->rts_threshold = 2347;
 
 	hw->queues = AC_MAX;
